    },
    {
      "num": "04 · the takeaway",
      "heading": "Reliable AI feels boring at the boundary",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">The inside can be probabilistic. The edge of the system should look like software: typed, validated, observable, and honest when it cannot comply.</p>"
        },
